msgctxt "68_Businessman"
msgid "Hm... There <Italic>was</Italic> something going on over here earlier. I could hear the shouting from all the way over on Nakamichi Street."
msgstr "Mmm... Algo <Italic>estaba</Italic> pasando por aquí hace un momento. Podía escuchar los gritos desde la calle Nakamichi."

msgctxt "80_Businessman"
msgid "I didn't see it myself, though. Not a chance I'd be standing here now if I had!"
msgstr "Pero no vi nada. ¡No estaría aquí parado si lo hubiera hecho!"

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey, you got a second?"
msgstr "Disculpe, ¿tiene un momento?"

msgctxt "104_Businessman"
msgid "Er... sure. How can I help you?"
msgstr "Claro... ¿Cómo puedo ayudar?"

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "Did you see a group of yakuza come by here maybe two, three hours ago?"
msgstr "¿Vio a un grupo de yakuzas pasar por aquí hace dos o tres horas?"

msgctxt "128_Businessman"
msgid "Yakuza!?"
msgstr "¡¿Yakuzas?!"

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "You know you're in Kamurocho, right? That shouldn't be such a surprise. Oh, and they were probably dragging someone behind them."
msgstr "Bueno, en Kamurocho no es sorpresa. Probablemente llevaban a la fuerza alguien."

msgctxt "152_Businessman"
msgid "Hm... There <Italic>was</Italic> something going on over here earlier. I could hear the shouting from all the way over on Nakamichi Street."
msgstr "Mmm... Algo <Italic>estaba</Italic> pasando por aquí hace un momento. Podía escuchar los gritos desde la calle Nakamichi."

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "Nakamichi? So you didn't see anything, then?"
msgstr "¿Nakamichi? ¿Entonces no vio nada?"

msgctxt "176_Businessman"
msgid "Oh, heavens no. If I had, I certainly wouldn't be standing here now like nothing happened. I usually turn heel and run when I see fights breaking out."
msgstr "Por Dios, no. Si hubiera visto algo, hubiera salido corriendo."

msgctxt "188_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh, okay then. Thanks anyway."
msgstr "Eh, está bien. Gracias de todos modos."

